  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the impact of the 10-week Active and Healthy
      Families (AHF) intervention on body mass index (BMI) in Latino youth aged 5-12 years.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
