  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Aged 5-12 years

          -  Body mass index greater than or equal to the 85th percentile for age and sex

          -  Patients seen at Contra Costa County clinics participating in Active and Healthy
             Families

          -  Spanish speaking

          -  Parent of participant

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Previous participation in Active and Healthy Families
      </textblock>
